"title": "5360: justice, of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5360",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The moral righteousness of God is revealed in his laws and expressed in his judicial acts. God's commands and judgments meet perfect standards of justice, and his apportioning of punishments and rewards is also perfectly just. God's justice is impartial. Special praise is his for vindicating the penitent and the needy who have no human champions. Ultimately, all God's ways will be seen as just and equitable.</p>\n<h2>God's justice declared</h2>\n<h3>God the Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:15\">PSA 92:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:17\">1PE 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:3\">JOB 36:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:7\">PSA 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:8\">PSA 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:8\">ISA 61:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:5\">ZEP 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>God the Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1JN 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:8-Heb1:9\">HEB 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1-Ps72:4\">PSA 72:1–72:4</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7\">9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:3–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3\">ISA 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1-Mal3:3\">MAL 3:1–3:3</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:14\">ACT 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">1CO 1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>\n<h3>God the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8-John16:11\">JHN 16:8–16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:9\">ACT 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">EPH 4:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice described</h2>\n<h3>As impartial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:17\">1PE 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17\">DEU 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:19\">JOB 34:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:27\">DAN 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34\">ACT 10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:11\">ROM 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:6\">GAL 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:25\">COL 3:25</a></p>\n<h3>As inescapable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:3\">ROM 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:21-Ps68:23\">PSA 68:21–68:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:11\">JER 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:16-Jer16:18\">JER 16:16–16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:53\">JER 51:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:22\">LAM 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:1-Amos9:4\">AMO 9:1–9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:4\">OBA 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:2-Heb2:3\">HEB 2:2–2:3</a></p>\n<h3>As infallible</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:13\">HEB 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:3\">1SA 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:2\">PRO 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:2\">PRO 21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:12\">PRO 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2\">ROM 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:16\">ROM 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice desired</h2>\n<h3>By the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:19\">PSA 9:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:9\">JDG 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:6\">PSA 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:12-Ps10:14\">PSA 10:12–10:14</a></p>\n<h3>By those who are misrepresented</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:1\">PSA 26:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:15\">1SA 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:23-Ps35:24\">PSA 35:23–35:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice doubted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:17\">MAL 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:29\">JOB 6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:2\">JOB 27:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:5\">JOB 34:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:2-Ps73:14\">PSA 73:2–73:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:11\">ECC 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:14\">ECC 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:27\">ISA 40:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:14\">ROM 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:19-Rom9:20\">ROM 9:19–9:20</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice demonstrated</h2>\n<h3>In his demands for social justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:18\">DEU 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:20\">DEU 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:16-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:16–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:46-Luke20:47\">LUK 20:46–20:47</a></p>\n<h3>In his defence of the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:6\">PSA 103:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:2\">PSA 72:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:12\">PSA 140:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:22-Prov22:23\">PRO 22:22–22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:4\">ISA 11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:7-Luke18:8\">LUK 18:7–18:8</a></p>\n<h3>In his vindication of the righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:1-Ps17:2\">PSA 17:1–17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:5\">PSA 24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:8-Isa50:9\">ISA 50:8–50:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:17\">ISA 54:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:8\">ISA 61:8</a></p>\n<h3>In the cross</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>In the resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a></strong></p>\n<h3>On the day of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5\">REV 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:7\">REV 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:2\">REV 19:2</a></p>",
